title: Auburn beat writers weigh in on quarterback competition
text:
comments Auburn beat writers weigh in on quarterback competition Auburn beat writers on quarterback situation Auburn beat writers Wes Sinor and James Crepea talk quarterbacks after practice Monday, Oct. 12, 2015, in Auburn, Ala. (Julie Bennett/jbennett@al.com) 
Auburn beat writers Wes Sinor and James Crepea talk about the quarterback competition between Jeremy Johnson and Sean White today after hearing from head coach Gus Malzahn in Auburn, Ala.
